      },
      "text": "### 핵심 기술스택\n- **Multi-Region ALB**\n- **Redis Cluster**\n- **MySQL Sharding**\n- **Kafka**\n- **Elasticsearch Cluster**\n- Kubernetes",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 280,
      "x": 520,
      "y": 750
